snippet: Grand Band, a group of six new-music pianists who first played together at the Bang on the Can Marathon in June, gave its second performance Tuesday night at Le Poisson Rouge.
abstract: Zachary Woolfe reviews performance by piano sextet Grand Band at Le Poisson Rouge.
lead_paragraph: Grand Band, a group of six new-music pianists who first played together at the Bang on the Can Marathon in June, gave its second performance Tuesday night at Le Poisson Rouge.
